							High-quality plating solutions at cost-effective rates, delivering value.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>

			<!-- Plant & Facility Images -->
			<section class='grid gap-8'>
				<h2 class='text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight'>Our Plant & Facilities</h2>
				<div class='grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3'>
					<div
						class='group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-white/10 bg-white/70 dark:bg-white/5'
